This is Perl module template for using Ingy's modern module style.

It includes:

* Module::Package
* Test::Common
* Stardoc

It should likely be installed under your main pkg/perl/ directory.

For example:

    cd $HOME/src/pkg/perl/
    git clone https://github.com/rafl/perl-dzil-pkg.git dzil
    cd $HOME/src/
    pkg new --from=pkg/perl/dzil --module=Foo::Bar foo-bar-pm

